00:00:15,194 --> 00:00:16,246
Roll call.

2
00:00:16,246 --> 00:00:20,277
Mr. Miller. Here. Mr. Behram. Here. Ms. Heckman. Here. Mr. Ford.

3
00:00:20,277 --> 00:00:23,404
Mr. Ford is excused. Mr. Wallace. Here. Mr. Davis. Here.

4
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,018
Hear item 2. Invocation pledge of allegiance.

5
00:00:27,018 --> 00:00:33,557
The invocation of this evening will be given by Imam Rashad Khalifa of the Islamic mosque of Tucson.

6
00:00:33,557 --> 00:00:37,020
Will you please remain standing for the pledge of allegiance to the flag?

7
00:00:42,306 --> 00:00:45,533
In the name of God, the Most Gracious, the Most Merciful.

8
00:00:46,289 --> 00:00:48,902
Praise be to God, Lord of the universe.

9
00:00:49,318 --> 00:00:51,318
The Most Gracious, the Most Merciful.

10
00:00:51,892 --> 00:00:54,055
Master of the Day of Recompense.

11
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:58,751
Only You we worship. Only You we ask for help.

12
00:00:59,483 --> 00:01:01,857
Guide us in the right path.

13
00:01:02,190 --> 00:01:05,377
The path of those who deserve Your blessings.

14
00:01:05,377 --> 00:01:08,683
Not of those who incurred Your displeasure

15
00:01:08,683 --> 00:01:11,092
Nor of those who go astray.

16
00:01:11,092 --> 00:01:12,224
Amen.


